	<h1 class="title">澳大利亚想用一台会走的喷射炮来代替消防员……</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/113378/small/113378.jpg?1435590009" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">周韶宏 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-16 07:00:44 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19129/medium/19129.jpg?1450172792" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


